off the council and you'll get your dog.''
   Johanson, a three-term Republican council member, has kept her
position.
   Police have said that stealing a dog is punishable by up to a
year in jail, and extortion by a maximum of 15 years in jail.
Investigators said they think the call may be genuine because
relatively few people knew of the dog's disappearance at the time
the call was made.
