birth; Christopher Travis, 2 pounds, 10 ounces; Kathryn Mary, 3
pounds, 6{ ounces; and Lauren Elizabeth, 3 pounds, 6 ounces _
arrived within three minutes of each other.
   Mrs. Trizna is to be released from the hospital next week.
   And how is her husband?
   ``OK, I guess,'' he said. ``It hasn't sunk in yet.''
